result.execSummary:
The defendant Faithe Emaleigh Nicole Parins was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Faithe Emaleigh Nicole Parins is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Faithe Emaleigh Nicole Parins was found guilty of Possession of THC (2nd+ Offense), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
  • Faithe Emaleigh Nicole Parins was found guilty of Possession of Methamphetamine, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(g).
  • Faithe Emaleigh Nicole Parins was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Felony, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(b).
